 (250.01), <a href="/web/20180712203804/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375113&amp;fLockTerm=Diabetes+mellitus+without+mention+of+complication%2c+type+II+or+unspecified+type%2c+not+stated+as+uncontrolled">Diabetes mellitus without mention of complication, type II or unspecified type, not stated as uncontrolled</a>
